 The UI is divided into 2 parts. Left part contains 3 sections. The first section has a search bar and 2 buttons. One button opens a side menu and the other one switches between Music and Podcasts. The second section is called "Made For Marichka" and contains 5 tiles with different playlists. The third section is called "Popular with listeners of The Making of Modern Ukraine" and contains 5 tiles with different podcasts. The right part of the UI is the media player. It has an album cover of the current song, a play/pause button, a previous track button, a next track button, a volume slider, and a full screen button.